      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal straight-six engineering. Featuring the iconic S54B32 power plant, it delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated double-VANOS variable valve timing system. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring a documented reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission that provides crisp, tactile gear synchronization. The variable M-differential lock remains tight, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This specimen exhibits zero mechanical fatigue, maintaining original factory tolerances throughout the drivetrain and suspension geometry. A true collector-grade machine for the discerning purist who demands mechanical transparency.",
